%% Diagram: Virtualization scroll loop sequence
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Container as Scroll Container
    participant Calc as Visible Range Calculator
    participant Pool as DOM Node Pool
    participant Body as Rendered Body

    User->>Container: scroll wheel / touch
    Container-->>Calc: scrollTop, clientHeight
    Calc->>Calc: derive [startIndex, endIndex] (+ overscan)
    Calc-->>Pool: requested row indices
    Pool->>Pool: recycle off-screen rows, hydrate new ones
    Pool-->>Body: positioned absolute rows
    Body-->>User: paint within next frame
    Note over Calc,Body: Total budget: 16 ms per frame at 60 Hz
